(1, 'About', 'about', '<!-- ======= Main article section ======= -->\n<div class=\"entry-img\"><img src=\"http://laracms.local/cms_assets/about/Pic-in-about-page-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\" /></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"entry-content\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 30px;\">\n<p><b>ERA-InfoTech Ltd</b> -A Joint Venture IT Company formed by Bank Asia Ltd, Ranks ITT Ltd of Bangladesh and Sash Tech SG Pte. Ltd, Singapore. ERA commenced it&rsquo;s journey on 11th November, 2002. ERA has developed Centralized Real Time, Web Based Core Banking Solution both for Conventional &amp; Islamic, Agent Banking, Loan Originating &amp; Approval System, HR &amp; Payroll Management solution, ERP, Micro Finance solution, Mobile and System critical software for various business houses, including Banks, Multinational Companies and the Government. We have a large team of internationally certified software professionals with knowledge in Oracle, Microsoft, Java, etc. ERA has been a pioneer in developing several software solutions in the country. IT solutions for the government like Ektee Bari Ektee Khamar (EBEK) have taken ERA&rsquo;s capabilities to a different level and proves the diverse skill sets available in the company.</p>\n<p>ERA has achieved CMMI (Capability Maturity Model Integration) Dev.Level 3, ISO-9001:2015 (Quality Management System) &amp; ISO-27001:2013 (Information Security Management System). ERA is a member of Bangladesh Association of Software and Information Services (BASIS).</p>\n<p>ERA has achieved National Productivity &amp; Quality Excellence Award 2015 from National Productivity Organization (NPO), Ministries of Industries, Government of The People&rsquo;s Republic of Bangladesh. Also achieved Manthan Award, India, South Asia and Asia Pacific 2013 in Business and Financial Inclusion Category &amp; International Leadership in Quality by BID, Paris, France. ERA is committed to deliver quality products and services to it&rsquo;s valued clients.</p>\n</div>\n<!-- End Main article section --> <!-- ======= Services Section ======= -->\n<div class=\"row gy-4 services\">\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6\" data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-delay=\"200\">\n<div class=\"service-box blue\"><i class=\"ri-discuss-line icon\"></i>\n<h3>Our Vision</h3>\n<p>To reinvent the way people use technology in their daily lives, empowering communities, for a better future.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6\" data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-delay=\"300\">\n<div class=\"service-box orange\"><i class=\"ri-discuss-line icon\"></i>\n<h3>Our Mission</h3>\n<p>To serve clients through integrated solutions by designing and developing the best and most efficient software through emphasizing the mutual relationship between technology and innovations.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- End Services Section -->', 'about', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2021-09-18 15:12:20'),
(2, 'Management', 'management', '<section class=\"team\">\n<div class=\"row gy-4\">\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center\"><a href=\"http://laracms.local/pages/chairman\">\n<div class=\"member\">\n<div><img src=\"http://laracms.local/cms_assets/front_page/managements/team-1.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"A. ROUF CHOWDHURY, CHAIRMAN\" /></div>\n<div class=\"member-info\">\n<h4>A. ROUF CHOWDHURY</h4>\n<span>CHAIRMAN</span></div>\n</div>\n</a></div>\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center\"><a href=\"http://laracms.local/pages/director\">\n<div class=\"member\">\n<div><img src=\"http://laracms.local/cms_assets/front_page/managements/team-2.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"NAFEES KHUNDKER, DIRECTOR\" /></div>\n<div class=\"member-info\">\n<h4>NAFEES KHUNDKER</h4>\n<span>DIRECTOR</span></div>\n</div>\n</a></div>\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center\"><a href=\"http://laracms.local/pages/chief-executive-officer\">\n<div class=\"member\">\n<div><img src=\"http://laracms.local/cms_assets/front_page/managements/team-3.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"MR. MD. SERAJUL ISLAM, FCMA, CHIEF EXECUTIVE OFFICER\" /></div>\n<div class=\"member-info\">\n<h4>MR. MD. SERAJUL ISLAM, FCMA</h4>\n<span>CHIEF EXECUTIVE OFFICER</span></div>\n</div>\n</a></div>\n</div>\n</section>', 'management', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2021-10-14 10:53:19'),
(3, 'Core Banking Platform', 'core-banking-platform', '<p class=\"d-flex justify-content-center\"><img src=\"http://laracms.local/cms_assets/products/core_banking_platform/iStelar-Logo.png\" alt=\"istelar\" class=\"img-fluid\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>We have been Serving Banks &amp; Financial institutions towards their digital future for more than 17 years.</strong></p>\n<p>Our Core Banking Solution- iStelar will help your bank to develop a customer-centric business model, simplify oprations, enable innovation and manage risk and compliance effectively.</p>\n<p>New age features of this solution contain Deposit, Loans, Teller Oprations, Account Maintenance, Trade Finance, Clearing Oprations, Remittance, SMS, Mobile &amp; Internet Banking, Electronic Collection (EFT &amp; RTGS) &amp; BACH. Compliant with Industry Standard messaging protocols like ISO, SWIFT &amp; Anti-Money Laundering.</p>\n<p>It is a proven platform for Growth &amp; Innovation which supports Multi Channel ADCs like ATM, POS, NPSB and more. Our converged platform &amp; extensive multilevel securities offer a range of services to meet various financial needs of every consumer segment, along with tools and add-ons that drive cost efficiencies while strengthening customer loyalty.</p>\n<p><strong>Features &amp; Benefits: </strong></p>\n<p><strong>Smarter. More Agile. More intelligent. More Automated.</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Customer-On Boarding.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Transactions management</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Allows to offer the right products at the right time</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">A holistic view of customer relationships through a centralized databaseEnabling straight-through processing and real-time capabilities to reduce costs</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Enabling straight-through processing and real-time capabilities to reduce costs</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Flexible Product Definition</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Compliant with industry standard messaging protocols like ISO, SWIFT</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Compliant with industry standard messaging protocols like ISO, SWIFT</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Anti-Money laundering compliant</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">BASEL framework compatible</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Extensive multilevel security</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Supports Multi Channel ADCs like ATM, POS, NPSB and more</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Lower TCO &amp; quick ROI</div>\n</li>\n</ul>', 'core banking platform', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2021-10-14 10:54:37'),
(4, 'Islamic Banking', 'islamic-banking', '<p class=\"d-flex justify-content-center\"><img src=\"http://laracms.local/cms_assets/products/islamic_banking/hikmah.png\" alt=\"hikmah\" class=\"img-fluid\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<p>HIKMAH is a comprehensive Islamic Banking Solution developed by ERA <strong>based on Core Principals of Sharia</strong>. It offers the industry&rsquo;s widest range of software solutions to Islamic banks addressing all their Business &amp; Operational requirements.</p>\n<p>HIKMAH provides Real Time Shariah Banking. Profit Distribution process is driven by a set of parameters that allow the users to group profit received from investment such as (Bai-Murabaha, HPSM etc.) with payable expense generated from liability business activity such as (Mudaraba accounts). Allow special profit distribution as per agreed ratio. Support both <strong>ISR &amp; Weighted Average Method</strong> in Profit Calculation.</p>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-12\">\n<h5>Features:</h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Integrated Modular Based System</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Global Limit Management</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Support Multi-Currency</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Support Multi Layer Chart of Accounts</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Central Process Management</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Extensive Audit Trail</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">AML Screening Compatible</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">BASEL Framework Compatible</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Omni Channel Account Opening</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Facilitate Window / Virtual Window Banking</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Extensive Multilevel Security</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Support Multi Channels</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Dynamic SMS Engine</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">User Friendly Interface</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Comprehensive MIS</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Responsive UI</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-12\">\n<h5>Unique Features:</h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Income Sharing Ratio Based Profit Distribution</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">User Defined Field Add option</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Dynamic Report Engine</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Smart Report Search Tool</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Dynamic Approval option</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Comprehensive Audit Trail</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Chat-Box Helpdesk</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Seamless Integration through RESTful/SOAP API</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>', 'islamic banking', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2021-10-14 10:55:30'),
(5, 'Loan Origination & Approval', 'loan-origination-approval', '<p class=\"d-flex justify-content-center\"><img src=\"http://laracms.local/cms_assets/products/loan_origination_and_approval/ocas.png\" alt=\"ocas\" class=\"img-fluid\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<p>Investing in a system that allows you to make lending quickly and accurately will make you stand out from the competition. ERA offers a highly flexible Loan Processing and Approval System for Corporate, Retail &amp; SME loan products. Beginning with capturing of credit requests, documents archiving, field investigation, financial analysis, CRG calculation and route them through a user defined workflow, OCAS gives users the control, flexibility and dynamic workflow necessary to faster loan processing.</p>\n<h5>Features:</h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Role based Workflow: Reduce loan processing time &amp; costs by routing applications through a role-based automated workflow.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Document Management: Capture and preserve required documents through archiving.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Automation of Credit Risk Assessment and Credit Decisions: By capturing all financial data, OCAS can automate the calculation of CRG and Financial Analysis.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Improve risk control: There is no risk of errors in the lending process, as the system ensures data accuracy and consistency.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Standardized &amp; Centralized: Automation of loan origination gives the HQ of the organization the flexibility to access the exact same data of any geo location.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Modular &amp; Comprehensive: Integration with other system makes it a comprehensive and modular system which will help the automation of entire process.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Customizable &amp; Flexible: Highly scalable, customizable and flexible in nature.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Retail, Corporate &amp; SME Lending: Supports all type of credit segments from Retail, SME and Corporate Loans.</div>\n</li>\n</ul>', 'loan origination approval', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2021-10-14 10:56:20'),
(6, 'Core Platform for NBFIs', 'core-platform-for-nbfis', '<p class=\"d-flex justify-content-center\"><img src=\"http://laracms.local/cms_assets/products/core_platform_for_nbfis/e-finance.png\" alt=\"E-Finance\" class=\"img-fluid\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<p>Core Financial Solution (E-FS) is an Online, Real-time Core System for Non-Banking Financial Institutes (NBFIs). It is a Functionally Rich software by which users can introduce new products, manage existing ones, manage cheques, perform EFTs, etc. on the go.</p>\n<p>We developed E-FS &ndash; Core Financial Solution for NBFIs from scratch following the principals and guidelines provided by Central Bank of Bangladesh for NBFIs. It is a complete solution for your Ultimate Digitalization Needs.</p>\n<h5><strong>Features:</strong></h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\"><strong>Extensive Financial Product Coverage</strong> &ndash; The system supports deposits and loans with complex features ranging from simple services to more advanced and sophisticated corporate products with added features.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\"><strong>Extensive Multilevel Security / Robust Security</strong> &ndash; Modern security measures like MFA, OTP, Bio-metric, complex password rules etc.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\"><strong>High Degree of Scalability</strong> &ndash; Easy expansion of the system by adding extra modules.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\"><strong>Integration</strong> &ndash; Enable back-office connectivity with multiple external systems and delivery channels using web services.</div>\n</li>\n</ul>', 'core platform, nbfis', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2021-10-14 10:56:47'),
(7, 'Microfinance', 'microfinance', '<p class=\"d-flex justify-content-center\"><img src=\"http://laracms.local/cms_assets/products/microfinance/bdesh.png\" alt=\"Bdesh\" class=\"img-fluid\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<p>Ektee Bari Ektee Khamar i.e. One House One Farm is a poverty alleviation project of the government of Bangladesh through e-financial inclusion followed by family farming livelihood and income generation of the under privileged and poor of the country. ERA-InfoTech Ltd. has to come up with a solution that can not only monitor the Loan related process but also has the ability to analyze the real time scenario of the project.</p>\n<p>ERA developed EBdesh Micro Finance Solution, a full-featured web application powered by a variety of advanced technologies that provides a real time Monitoring with Management dashboard.</p>\n<p>ERA has achieved Manthan Award South Asia and Asia Pacific 2013 in Business and Financial Inclusion Category for its EBdesh- Micro Finance Solution.</p>\n<h5><strong>Features:</strong></h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Bio-metric enrollment</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Centralized administration</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Audit trail on all transaction</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Dash-board driven information</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Online daily consolidated reports</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Fully real time web-based solution</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Highly customized and parameterized</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Unlimited member of groups and users</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Quick and easy data backup and restore</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Each operation is mapped with a unique ID</div>\n</li>\n</ul>', 'microfinance', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2021-10-14 10:57:16'),
(8, 'Agent Banking', 'agent-banking', '<p class=\"d-flex justify-content-center\"><img src=\"http://laracms.local/cms_assets/products/agent_banking/Agent-Logo.png\" alt=\"Agent\" class=\"img-fluid\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<p>ERA develops Agent Banking Solution to provide banking services to unbanked people, bring mass rural people under Financial Inclusion, involve ICT innovations, capture data through Bio-metric technology and enhance green technology. Agent banking transactions are done on real time basis and integrated with Bank&rsquo;s Core Banking solution. Customers get instant confirmation of transaction through Mobile SMS and system generated Printed money receipts.</p>\n<h5><strong>Solution Overview:</strong></h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Customer Acquisition</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">User Management</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Agent Management</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Agent Banking</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Audit Trail</div>\n</li>\n</ul>', 'agent-banking', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2021-10-14 10:57:42'),
(9, 'Cheque Processing & EFT', 'cheque-processing-eft', '<p class=\"d-flex justify-content-center\"><img src=\"http://laracms.local/cms_assets/products/cheque_processing_and_eft/micr.png\" alt=\"micr\" class=\"img-fluid\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<p>ERA-InfoTech Ltd has developed e-MICR solution under the guideline of Central Bank of Bangladesh which is a Centralized Online Automatic Cheque Processing System. It helps banks to meet legal and regulatory requirement, reduces cheque processing costs, improve productivity with automated technical verification, reduce mitigates risk and eliminates delays.</p>\n<h5><strong>Features:</strong></h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Centralized Online Electronic Fund Transfer System.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Data can be storage centralized.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Supports various distributed operating system.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Oracle database server for both front office as well as back office operation Independent of the back office.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Outward clearing likes upload data and image from scanner, data entry by maker, data verifications by checker, and Inward Clearing likes Upload Data and Image From PBM, Collect Data, Branch Wise Distribution, Branch Wise Distribution process are automatically functionalized.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Client Communication through mail or SMS.</div>\n</li>\n</ul>', 'cheque-processing-eft', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2021-10-14 10:58:14'),
(10, 'Anti-Money Laundering', 'anti-money-laundering', '<p class=\"d-flex justify-content-center\"><img src=\"http://laracms.local/cms_assets/products/anti_money_laundering/money-laundering.png\" alt=\"anti-money-laundering\" class=\"img-fluid\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<p>ERA&rsquo;s Anti-Money Laundering (AML) System has been designed for a Financial Institute to monitor or control the money laundering as per guideline of central bank. ERA&rsquo;s AML will minimize the money laundering activities by automating the Blacklist Screening interface with CBS.</p>\n<h5><strong>Features:</strong></h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\"><strong>Blacklist Screening System</strong> &ndash; Allows banks and other financial institutions to monitor transaction on a real time basis.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\"><strong>Off-line Blacklist Screening System</strong> &ndash; Allows banks and other financial institutions to monitor transaction on a daily/weekly/monthly basis.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\"><strong>Search options</strong> &ndash; Phonetics Search, Fuzzy Search, Exact Match Search</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\"><strong>Security</strong> &ndash; Multiple Level Authorization for Blacklist Screenings</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\"><strong>False Positive Management</strong> &ndash; Reduce false positive detection and increase efficient detection of money-laundering.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\"><strong>Integration with online black list data sources</strong> &ndash; On-line Black List Data uploading System (OFAC, UN, EU, etc.)</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\"><strong>Black list Data Management</strong> &ndash; Supports offline file upload (XML, CSV, Excel etc.)</div>\n</li>\n</ul>', 'anti-money-laundering', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2021-10-14 10:58:43'),
(11, 'Customer On-boarding & e-KYC', 'customer-on-obarding-e-kyc', '<p>Client onboarding is an entire process which users go through when they start their journey as a customer of a bank. The process which is followed in banks involves multiple departments within the organization like front office, operations, risk, legal, credit, compliance, tax and more performing various functions.</p>\n<p>ERA&rsquo;s eKYC is a paperless and online solution comprising various integrated components to help businesses in next-generation customer journeys through realization of digital ID verification. e-KYC solution which deals with electronic customer onboarding, identification and verification of customer identity, creating of customer digital KYC profile as well as risk grading of customers in a digital means.</p>\n<p>The sole purpose of this application is to use the Election Commission SDK for Fingerprint &amp; Photo verification. It facilitates banks for Regulatory compliance through authenticated source , Fraud prevention, Operational ease and Interfacing capability with CBS, ABS, Loan Process, ATM, Credit Card etc. for customers on boarding.</p>', 'customer-on-obarding-e-kyc', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2021-10-14 10:59:17'),
(12, 'Treasury Management', 'treasury-management', '<p class=\"d-flex justify-content-center\"><img src=\"http://laracms.local/cms_assets/products/treasury_management/tesoro.png\" alt=\"tesoro\" class=\"img-fluid\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<p>A full suite of Treasury Modules support the trading of a wide range of domestic and international financial instruments including foreign exchange, Fund Requisition and Management. These modules assist dealers in deal capture, position maintenance / revaluation. The treasury module supports the various functional areas within the bank accounting, settlement &amp; messaging and management information.</p>\n<h5><strong>Features:</strong></h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Dealer Management &ndash; manage activities related to dealers</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Counter Party Management &ndash; manage activities related to counter party</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Fund Management &ndash; perform fund management activities</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Limit Management &ndash; perform limit management activities</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">FX Dealings &ndash; all FX related dealings are handled</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Money Market &ndash; all money market transaction are managed</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Securities (Bill/Bonds) &ndash; purchase and sell bills and bonds</div>\